<div class="row profile-head">
    <div class="profile-header col-sm text">
        <h1>Travel <span class="brand-text">Monkey</span> User Profile</h1>
        <div>
            <h4>
                Welcome to your home.
            </h4>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <!-- Left Sidebar -->
        <div class="col-sm-3">

            <div id="LeftSideBar">
                <div class="SideBarItem">
                    <br><br>
                    <img src="/assets/img/pic/profile.jpg" alt="photo" height="250" width="250">
                </div>
                <div class="SideBarTitle">XXX's Profile<br><br>
                    <div class="SideBarItem">
                        <p>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" id="postButton"
                                    onclick="window.location.href='article.html'">
                                Add New Post
                            </button>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-sm-9">

            <div id="content_inside">

                <div class="singlePost">
                    <h3 class="entry_title">Post Title HERE!
                    </h3>
                    <div class="entry">
                        <div class="entry_date">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm"
                                    onclick="window.location.href='view.html'">View
                            </button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-sm"
                                    onclick="window.location.href='edit.html'">Edit
                            </button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm">Delete
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="imageComment_left" style="width:150px;height:150px">
                            <div class="imageComment_img">
                                <img src="/assets/img/index/cover3.jpg" height="150" width="150"
                                     alt="PostPicture"/>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="post_content">
                            <p>The CSS and XHTML of this design validates. It consists of a tableless
                                pure CSS layout. This is an open source design released under the BSD
                                License. However I would be grateful if you did not remove the link to
                                my site at the bottom of the page. If you would like to have this design
                                customised please visit my site for contact information.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="entryFooter">
                            Posted on {date}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <hr>
                </div>

                <div class="singlePost">
                    <h3 class="entry_title">Post Title HERE!
                    </h3>
                    <div class="entry">
                        <div class="entry_date">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm"
                                    onclick="window.location.href='view.html'">View
                            </button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-sm"
                                    onclick="window.location.href='edit.html'">Edit
                            </button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm">Delete
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="imageComment_left" style="width:150px;height:150px">
                                <div class="imageComment_img">
                                    <img src="/assets/img/index/cover2.jpg" height="150" width="150"
                                         alt="Preview"/>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="post_content">
                                <p>Ma quande lingues coalesce, li grammatica del resultant lingue es plu
                                    simplic e regulari quam ti del coalescent lingues. Li nov lingua franca
                                    va esser plu simplic e regulari quam li existent Europan lingues. It va
                                    esser tam simplic quam Occidental: in fact, it va esser Occidental. A un
                                    Angleso it va semblar un simplificat Angles, quam un skeptic Cambridge
                                    amico dit me que Occidental es.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="entryFooter">
                                Posted on {date}
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>


            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>